/* start query 67 in stream 0 using template query67.tpl */
SELECT
  *
FROM (
  SELECT
    i_category,
    i_class,
    i_brand,
    i_product_name,
    d_year,
    d_qoy,
    d_moy,
    s_store_id,
    sumsales,
    RANK() OVER (
      PARTITION BY i_category
      ORDER BY sumsales DESC
      ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW
    ) AS rk
  FROM derived_1
) AS dw2
WHERE
  rk <= 100
ORDER BY
  i_category,
  i_class,
  i_brand,
  i_product_name,
  d_year,
  d_qoy,
  d_moy,
  s_store_id,
  sumsales,
  rk
LIMIT 100
